Scenario 1:
Find specific no of   key words from all directory .Key words are 
like and dislike 

Algorithm
Read all files from a specified url.There can be multiple directories and sub directories 
Copy that files to BigDinosaur directories.
Read every files . Perform map reduce on every files .
On every files find out no of key words .
Aggregate all results from all files to get the total  no of words 

